reviewText: It was in great condition! It arrived as was expected without any problems! I very much recommend them! I am a very satisfied customer! Good Porn!

So your thinking of purchasing Welcome to Pia Carrot2
Well do not think to long. This is a rare gem and hard to find.
 Try to find Welcome to Pia Carrot the first set wile your at it and get both.
You won't regret it.
The caracters are fun and get into many strange situations.
If you have allready watced the first set you know all about that
Yes thier is some kinkiness but it is all very fun and fits into the story.
I watched  some of it dubed it was ok the voice actors did thier best.
I prefered the original Japanese with subtitles version. I gues that is one of my quirks.
Allmost forgot to mention the art quality is way up thier so it looks great to.
